            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報25544 ，跌139點或0.54%，低水123點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科指期貨開報5700 ，跌41點或0.71%，低水43點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國指期貨開報9201，跌63點或0.68%，低水57點。</p>\n</div>",
