            "title": "維立志博以35元定價　每手中籤率0.27%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生物科技企業維立志博(09887)公布招股結果，以發售價上限35元定價，集資淨額11.79億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：維立志博官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_LeadsBiolabs-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：維立志博官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/12/20241209_FI_source-web_LeadsBiolabs-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：維立志博官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">股份公開發售部分超額認購3493.78倍，認購每手100股，中籤率0.27%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">綜合3大暗盤場，輝立暗盤收70.05元，較招股價升35.05元或100.143%，未計手續費，一手100股帳面賺3,505元；耀才及富途暗盤同樣收69.75元，較招股價升34.75元或99.286%，未計手續費，一手100股帳面賺3,475元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120036-%e7%b6%ad%e7%ab%8b%e5%bf%97%e5%8d%9a%e4%bb%a535%e5%85%83%e5%ae%9a%e5%83%b9%e3%80%80%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e4%b8%ad%e7%b1%a4%e7%8e%870-27-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/09887.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-25 09:10:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "雲頂新耀折讓逾10%配股  集資近16億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">雲頂新耀(01952)宣布配股集資，配股價每股配售價69.7元，較上日收市價折讓約10.12%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_Hong_Kong_Trump_Tariffs-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司以先舊後新配售2256.1萬股，佔已發行股份6.87%，配售股份相當於擴大後已發行股本約6.43%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集資約15.73億元。公司表示，擬將配售所得款項淨額15.53億元的50%用於管線產品的全球研發；40%用於商業化推進工作，包括新產品上市及推廣；及10%用作公司營運及一般行政管理開支。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120299-%e9%9b%b2%e9%a0%82%e6%96%b0%e8%80%80%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%93%e9%80%be10%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1-%e9%9b%86%e8%b3%87%e8%bf%9116%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/01952.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-25 09:00:33",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "黑期跌88點   ADR低水133點  信義光能低水7.9%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">新加坡黑期跌88點或0.34%，報25539。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據高盛網站，港股ADR較恒指昨天收市低水133點或0.52%，報25533點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：信義光能官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/bplib_20230719-123531_source-web_00968-1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：信義光能官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">主要ADR幾全線報跌，信義光能(00968) ADR折合港元計收報3.01元，較香港收市價大幅低水7.9% ; 新東方(09901) ADR折合港元計收報3.01元，較香港收市價大幅低水3.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">理想汽車(02015) ADR折合港元計收報116.15元，較香港收市價低2.2% ; 比亞迪(01211) ADR較香港收市價低水1.1%，折合130.64港元</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988) ADR折合港元計收報118.88元，較香港收市價低1.2% ; 美團(03690) ADR較香港收市價低0.8%，折合133.34港元 ;騰訊(00700) ADR折合港元計收報552.67元，較香港收市價高0.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報102.02元，較香港收市價低0.2% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣70.99元，較香港收市價低水0.4% ;港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣445.9元，較香港收市價低0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">僅中通快遞(02057)ADR高水，折合港幣158.89元，較香港收市價高水0.4%。攜程(09961)ADR折合港幣506.66元，平水。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報25505點，跌178點，較昨日恒指收市25667點，低水162點，成交12386張。國指夜市期指收報9194點，較昨日國指收市低水64點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120290-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e8%b7%8c88%e9%bb%9e-adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4133%e9%bb%9e-%e4%bf%a1%e7%be%a9%e5%85%89%e8%83%bd%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b47-9",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-3.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-07-25 08:55:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "韓股初段變動不大",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">南韓股市在開市初段變動不大，首爾綜合指數較早時報3192點，升1點，升幅0.05%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15120278-%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%ae%8a%e5%8b%95%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a7-29",
